    title: "Best Home Buyer App 2026: Flood Zone, Permits, and Comps in One Place",
    metaDescription: "Looking for the best home buyer app in 2026? See why PropertyDNA tops the list for flood zone data, permit history, and real comps — free on iOS.",
    date: "2026-06-12",
